---
title: Mild Thai Red Curry Pork Meatball Soup with Roasted Veggies & Baby Leaves
description: Get cosy with this Thai-inspired meal! Our mild Thai red curry paste brings flavour and heat to this comforting bowl of soup, all brought together with tender pork meatballs, creamy coconut milk and roasted veggies. It’s rich and mellow, with just the right amount of heat to keep things interesting!
